Subprog AS_NBLIG
Local Decimal BASPAG
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(49234,GBOUT1) From OBJDIV
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_NBLIG From W1VCONGE
Gosub _AFF
End

Subprog B1_NBLIG
Local Decimal BASPAG
If !GWEBSERV
 ## Action STD
 Call B1_NBLIG From VCONGE
Endif
If mkstat=99 : mkstat = 0 : Elsif mkstat=0 : mkstat = 2 : Endif
Gosub _AFF
End

